'Version 1.0.3. Minor. 20230912. Added code to measure 3 Stevens probes, 3 Acclima 305 sensors, and 3 acclima 310 sensors. Also added code so that either the 3.4m or 5.4m beaded stream cable will
'onsite.
'Version 1.0.4. Minor. 20231011. Divide the neutron counts by 10 since they can exceed 7999. This is an issue with the FP2 rules which limit values to +/-7999.
'Version 1.0.5. Minor. 20231025. Moved the Sommer SD reading to 59 minutes (1 minute before the hour), noticed the reading is from previous hour. Believe this is because
'of the time interval for the measurement (10s reading).
'Verson 1.0.6. 20231121. Made slight tweaks to the ordering of SDI-12 sensor readings to optimize based on measurement duration. They all fire with no errors, or missed scans,
'Version 2.0.0. IN-DEVELOPMENT. Integrated a time check for GOES which will automatically set the CR1000X clock if the drift is beyond a certain threshold. Refined the Beaded Stream process
'and associated comm port open/close. Removed HydroInnova Snow Fox, Removed SCAN Acclima310 sensor. Added BaroVUE BP subroutine. Added Geolux LX80-S subroutine. Split the SDI-12 sensors between two COM ports to reduce potential conflict with slow responding
'sensors. Added a second snow depth measurement at 58 minutes for the USH9 resample, and LX80-S measurement.
