'Version 3.0.1. 2025 Intitial Field Deployment. Programming modded to work with CR1000Xe datalogger with OS 8.2.1. Refined the functionality of the Net Rad Heater command code. Worked to better time the SDI-12 sensors so that there are no longer skipped scans
'and NANs showing up in the array(s). All SDI12 sensors, aside from soils, use the C command vs M command. All SDI-12 sensors will fill arrays with NAN when the sensor has issues reading.
